            "answer_text": "Let\u2019s try genetics. That\u2019s invariable and can mean a predisposition to mini-strokes and vascular dementia. Let\u2019s try environmental. If your spouse dies, you can become depressed and isolated. That will lead into a downward spiral. There. Now you have two ways that oldsters can slip into senility. I see it happen all around me in my senior housing. ",
